section: 4. Commercial Conditions

deadline: Tender validity expiry | date: 2026-08-30 | consequence: tender may be withdrawn or repriced
deadline: Bid bond submission | date: 2026-08-15 | consequence: bid declared non-responsive

warranty: Defects liability period on all works | owner: Tenderer | period: 365 days
warranty: Chiller plant performance guarantee | owner: Tenderer | period: 24 months

clause: Performance security | scope: Tenderer | requirement: 10% of contract sum, unconditional bank guarantee
clause: Advance payment | scope: Employer | requirement: 15% against equal advance-payment guarantee
clause: Liquidated damages | scope: Tenderer | requirement: 0.1% of contract sum per day, capped at 10%
clause: Price basis | scope: Tenderer | requirement: firm and fixed for the full contract period, no escalation

milestone: Practical completion of all works | date: 2027-12-20 | consequence: liquidated damages apply

payment-term: Monthly interim valuations | basis: measured work done, certified within 28 days, less 5% retention
payment-term: Retention release | basis: 50% at practical completion, 50% at end of defects liability period

section: 5. Authorization

text: This tender has been reviewed and is submitted for and on behalf of Al-Mirqab Construction & Engineering W.L.L. The sign-offs below are recorded pre-seal approvals; the document will be sealed and cryptographically signed prior to lodgement with the Employer.

